title: ValueError: Dimension 0 in both shapes must be equal, but are 1 and 255. Shapes are [1,1,1024,18] and [255,1024,1,1]. for 'Assign_360' (op: 'Assign') with input shapes: [1,1,1024,18], [255,1024,1,1].
body:
I'm getting this error when loading the pretrained weights. In another issue I saw, that I should downgrade batch size-> didn't work or downgrade tensorflow-> not necessary as I am using 1.13 ... Anyone here who knows the issue?
